    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The `_` syntax makes it a bit ugly.\n\nWhat about adding the templates in a nested attribute + copy it at root level if not defined:\n\n``` js\ndata.helpers = {};\nforEach(templateHelpers, function(method, name) {\n  data.helpers[name] = function() {\n    return function(value) {\n      return method(hogan.compile(value).render(data));\n    };\n  };\n  if (typeof data[name] === 'undefined') {\n    data[name] = data.helpers[name];\n  }\n});\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2015-09-15T11:49:15Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/90#issuecomment-140365942",
