    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I agree that the `_` might not be the best way, but the alternative of putting it in `helpers` makes templates very verbose `{{#helpers.formatNumber}}{{nbHits}}{{/helpers.formatNumber}}`. Don't know which is best.\n\nAnyway, I think we should chose one of the two ways and not both.\n",
